<p align="justified">
  <h4>Welcome to SheInnovates</h4><br/>
   <strong>Last updated: [06 August 2023]</strong><br/>
  We are committed to protecting your privacy and providing a safe and secure experience while using our app.
  This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information. By using our app, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.<br /><br />

  <strong>Information We Collect</strong><br/>
