  <strong>Data Security</strong><br/>
  We implement security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access and use. However, no data transmission over the internet or electronic storage method is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.<br/>

  <strong>Children's and Men Privacy</strong><br />
  SheInnovates is not intended for children under the age of 13 or any males.If we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under 13 or a male, we will take appropriate steps to delete the information as soon as possible.<br />

  <strong>Your Choice</strong><br/>
  You can review and update your personal information by accessing your account settings within the app.<br /><br />

  <strong>Changes to this Privacy Policy</strong><br /><br />
  We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The most current version will be posted on our app, and the date of the latest revision will be indicated at the top of this page. We encourage you to review the Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we collect, use, and protect your information.
</p>
